Sinopse: Thomas Dunn has lost his faith after his young daughter's death. His life has crumbled and his confidence is shattered. Yet, on this day he awakens to discover that his loving wife Mandy is finally pregnant again. Maybe this is their chance to move away from the tragedy of the past and for him to find his faith again. But it is on this day that a large alien mothership appears in the heavens and the people of Earth are suddenly plagued with visions of the end of civilization. Tom and Mandy are split up as the mothership launches a massive alien fleet which attack the towns and cities of Earth. Tom must look deep within himself to find not just his faith but the wisdom and strength to save the human race from the horrors that threaten them. However, first he must find Mandy, as he discovers that their new baby holds the key to the future of humanity. The battle lines are drawn and the final stance for Earth is about to begin.—SC
